"Telekinetic Storm" 
        This is an impressive attack based on the concepts behind the
        Ballistic Attack power.  The damage it causes is based solely
        on what you are carrying at the time.  It will take everything
        in your inventory that you aren't wearing or wielding and hurl
        it at the target in a single, giant telekinetic attack.  It can
	make it either very expensive or very cheap, depending on how 
	much you are carrying at the time.
 
SP Cost:  25		Guild Level:  4		Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  tstorm <target>
